  "style": "APA",
  "texts": [
    "The second concern, \"academic integrity and ethical use\" relates to concerns related to the ethical use of GAI tools like plagiarism and originality, transparent use, and privacy of data.",
    "Concerns related to the impact on researchers' skills and research innovation were grouped under the \"dependence on AI\" theme.",
    "The fourth aspect discussed by researchers was the \"data privacy and security\" of GAI tools and subdivided into, handling of complex data and context window size.",
    "Findings indicate that the \"accuracy and bias\" of the GAI-generated content is a significant concern among researchers.",
    "This aspect is related to data erroneous like factual inaccuracies and irrelevant content which is a highly threatening factor to academic research standards (Abdelhafiz et al., 2024; Abuyaman, 2023; Alkaissi & McFarlane, 2023; Bond et al., 2024)."
  ],
